OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773349951
OL,3,CWoman suffers gunshot wound to leg in
OL,4,C'targeted' shooting
OL,6,FA woman has suffered a gunshot wound
OL,7,Fto her leg after "targeted" shooting
OL,8,Fin the early hours of the morning.
OL,10,FArmed officers were called to Lime
OL,11,FGrove, in Toxteth, Liverpool, at
OL,12,Fapproximately 12:55am on Thursday, 12
OL,13,FMarch, and discovered a woman in her
OL,14,F20s injured.
OL,16,FThe victim was transported to a local
OL,17,Fhospital for assessment, Merseyside
OL,18,FPolice said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/4
