CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773349951
OL,3,CWoman suffers gunshot wound to leg in
OL,4,C'targeted' shooting
OL,6,FA significant police presence remains
OL,7,Fin the area as forensic teams, house-
OL,8,Fto-house enquiries, and CCTV searches
OL,9,Fare carried out by detectives.
OL,11,FDetective Inspector Ainsley McAlice
OL,12,Fdescribed the investigation as being
OL,13,Fin its "critical early stages."
OL,15,F"We are looking to establish exactly
OL,16,Fwhat happened, where it happened, and
OL,17,Fto find the person responsible," DI
OL,18,FMcAlice said.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/4
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1773349951
OL,3,CWoman suffers gunshot wound to leg in
OL,4,C'targeted' shooting
OL,6,F"We understand the concern that any
OL,7,Fsuch incident will have in our
OL,8,Fcommunities, and initially believe
OL,9,Fthat this was a targeted attack by
OL,10,Fsomeone known to the victim."
OL,12,FOfficers are particularly interested
OL,13,Fin speaking with anyone who saw
OL,14,Findividuals fleeing the scene toward
OL,15,FLodge Lane or Sefton Park.
OL,17,FLocal residents are being urged to
OL,18,Fcheck their doorbell cameras and
OL,19,Fprivate CCTV for any suspicious
OL,20,Factivity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/4
